port editors/encryptpad
type port
reason "dragonfly patches for build system and portability; Makefile.diff for build deps"
target @any

patch apply diffs/Makefile.diff

file materialize dragonfly/patch-deps_makefiles_build.mak -> dragonfly/patch-deps_makefiles_build.mak
file materialize dragonfly/patch-deps_makefiles_platform.mak -> dragonfly/patch-deps_makefiles_platform.mak
file materialize dragonfly/patch-deps_plog_include_plog_Util.h -> dragonfly/patch-deps_plog_include_plog_Util.h
file materialize dragonfly/patch-deps_stlplus_portability_build.cpp -> dragonfly/patch-deps_stlplus_portability_build.cpp
